## APPLICATION ATTRIBUTION

### Lucide Icons

- https://lucide.dev/
- https://github.com/lucide-icons/lucide
- ISC License
- Copyright (c) Lucide Icons and Contributors
- see ### lucide-isc below

Icons bundled from `lib/icons/lucide/`: `arrow-up`, `chevron-left`, `chevron-right`, `chevrons-left`, `chevrons-right`, `circle-power`, `cog`, `heart`, `info`, `keyboard`, `pin`, `puzzle`, `rotate-cw`, `settings`, `shield-check`, `trash-2`, `undo-2`.

The following bundled Lucide icons are derived from the Feather project (see ### feather-mit below): `arrow-up`, `chevron-left`, `chevron-right`, `chevrons-left`, `chevrons-right`, `info`, `trash-2`.

